{"tid":494820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓人乘幽靈船赴日偷電器　被捕時激烈反抗","createTime":"2017-12-10T05:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T12:52:47.000Z","uid":41818,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1945b8492d8ca27c083ec6a55f4bfe88761553e1","tid":494820,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171209/640_6c5b0664acfbf34ea82a921ba699b93e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171209%2F640_6c5b0664acfbf34ea82a921ba699b93e.jpg&h=27c21286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171209/640_962c0de0a7b3c4b7966d336926bce395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171209%2F640_962c0de0a7b3c4b7966d336926bce395.jpg&h=44ee5c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171209/640_09c9d8085b67310f430a2f16ebe63d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171209%2F640_09c9d8085b67310f430a2f16ebe63d46.jpg&h=ad9c5d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓人乘幽靈船赴日偷電器，被捕時激烈反抗。翻自YouTube<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北韓一艘「幽靈船」在上月底漂流到日本北海道的松前小島，島上有一些日本漁民搭建的臨時小屋，但屋內的電器幾乎都被偷走，日本警方相信搭乘這艘「幽靈船」的3名北韓男子涉嫌重大，在今日將其逮捕，但當中有人還激烈反抗。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《朝日新聞台》報導，上月有10名北韓人搭著這艘木造「幽靈船」來到松前小島，之後日本海巡署將這艘船引導至函館港停泊，並進行調查。但就在昨日下午3時左右，固定船隻的繩索全部被切斷，這艘「幽靈船」也駛離函館港逃跑，之後日本警方發現，大約追捕了1小時左右再度將船隻扣押，並押回函館港。<br />\n<br />\n今日早晨日本警方以竊盜罪嫌，逮捕45歲船長姜明學以及2名船員，警方認為這3人有逃亡之虞，但他們被捕時一度做出激烈反抗，警方也相信他們偷走約總價值1千萬日圓(約新台幣280萬元)的電器與發電機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171209/1256260/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171209%2F1256260%2F&d=ePCWnjtSfoUi8ES%2FkCpDS26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7a55f07d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171209%2F1256260%2F&h=0aabd401\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171209/1256260/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fSv9dlKLnPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfSv9dlKLnPM&d=ePCWnjtSfoUi8ES%2FkCpDS26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=40b1e33f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fSv9dlKLnPM</a>"},{"pid":"7d7eb27d32b935680d1f5f08471d33f0fb278520","tid":494820,"uid":98431,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:49:04.000Z","msg":"唔交返D戲 返到北韓咪又係死 係日本做坐仲好"},{"pid":"eae9f2e7da5b4d1574a6fe443b3e7ecbc71bd988","tid":494820,"uid":33439,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"係日本坐監會唔會好過係北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140c7e8d4a2a8f3b2c9dbca804ebd65ff84c47cc","tid":494820,"uid":131020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"偷電器都偷左50萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放係船到？"},{"pid":"ad9f3f4ac4e61ae0ae36297c049f2e9f2399a4c4","tid":494820,"uid":57023,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"日本仔唔包容，未富先驕，電器共享有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00ac85051f8055c82389706b66c8941341bdab0","tid":494820,"uid":56999,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本坐監會唔會好過係北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該會唔願走"},{"pid":"d84b790d2a4e0ec282e6fc9daa836659b0f11664","tid":494820,"uid":42820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"另類脫北？"},{"pid":"e97280b568a9ebcec83e37508f649f0da4eee821","tid":494820,"uid":57023,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>